Develop an interest in music other than the current Top 40: classical pieces, opera, and early jazz. Bach, Mozart, Tchaikovsky, Wagner, and of course Beethoven are great composers to start with. In the way of popular music, the Universal Music Group publishes a series of CD compilations called 20th Century Masters, which accolades "the best of" great modern artists, such as Louis Armstrong and Chet Baker. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/1d/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/1d/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-760px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Read regularly, especially the news and literary classics. Know what is happening in the news (subscribe to and skim through TIME magazine or The Economist) and read contemporary novels geared towards society and your generation. Read poetry and also visit book stores and pick up novels by the great authors. (Tolstoy, Dickens, Hemingway, etc. are all respected but look for things that interest you. ){"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/45/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/45/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Get a basic understanding of the visual arts, including painting, sculpture, and architecture. Learn about aesthetics, art theory, criticism, and other related topics. Travel to see famous paintings and buildings in person if you can spare the expense. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7c/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7c/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-760px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Attend presentations of the performing arts, such as theater plays, ballets and operas. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b0/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b0/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet4.jpg/v4-760px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Learn about the art of film. Purchase a movie guide. Rent (and possibly buy) films of all genres. The cable channel Turner Classic Movies generally airs unedited, commercial-free classics, and The Criterion Collection distributes digitally restored DVDs of authoritative motion pictures. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/06/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet5.jpg/v4-460px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet5.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/06/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet5.jpg/v4-760px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet5.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Pick up side interests in other arts that pique your curiosity, such as, for example, culinary art (cooking and cuisine), decorative arts (furniture arrangement), and calligraphy (handwriting). {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/98/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet6.jpg/v4-460px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet6.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/98/Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet6.jpg/v4-760px-Be-a-Sophisticated-and-Cultured-Male-Step-1Bullet6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
